sentences.en: It was Ruper Brooke who asked if there was honey still for tea.
sentences.vi: Chính rupert brooke là người hỏi xem người ta còn mật ong cho trà không?

sentences.en: Minford, M., Quang, D., Nguyen, H. T. and Brooke, P. (2004) An Expenditure Tracking Study of the Hunger Eradication and Poverty Reduction Programme and Programme 135: Final Report, UNDP, Ha Noi.
